      • buildFromNodeWrapper

        public static DocumentData buildFromNodeWrapper(NodeWrapper nodeWrapper,
                                                java.lang.String uuid,
                                                java.lang.String nodeVersionUUID)
        builds a DocumentData instance off a NodeWrapper. Pay special attention to the way uuid's are juggled here!
        Parameters:
        nodeWrapper - - the NodeWrapper where all the main info comes
        uuid - - either the uuid value to be stored in the documentData instance or, if null, nodeWrapper.uuid will be stored
        nodeVersionUUID - - documentData.nodeVersionUUID
        Returns:
        documentData
